data.description: Come and see this cute 3 bedroom, 2 bath home located on just over an acre in Edgewood! Open floor plan, plenty of storage space in the kitchen. The primary bedroom is separate from the other bedrooms. Oversized garage with space for a workshop/hobby area or extra storage.  Views of South Mountain from the backyard.
